dct_title_s: Map of the West India & Bahama islands, with the adjacent coasts of Yucatan, Honduras, Caracas, &c.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Includes: Possessions of the European powers. Probably issued in: A popular atlas of the world ... London : Published by James Wyld ... , 1849.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published by James Wyld, geographer to the Queen, Charing Cross East, 1847.
